name: MarinHealth&HumanSvc
tweet: PREVENGA EL FRAUDE DE SU TARJETA EBT Evite que le roben sus beneficios: no comparta su número de tarjeta EBT o código secreto de PIN. Nunca nos comunicaremos con usted para pedirle que nos de su número de tarjeta o PIN.  https://t.co/XCKrF4dPxd

name: MarinHealth&HumanSvc
tweet: Fraud Alert! We have been receiving an increasing number of fraud reports about clients having their EBT Card information stolen.  ⚠️Do not share your EBT card number or PIN. We will NEVER contact you to ask you to provide your card or PIN numbers.  https://t.co/zF3Gm5Em2i
